biography:

After working as a Software Developer for a few years, Stefanie decided to shift her focus and ended up becoming a Machine Learning Engineer. She is passionate about ethical & just AI and likes to read and talk about it whenever she gets the chance. 
In order to inspire the next generation of AI users and developers, she organizes
and hosts workshops for kids and teenagers on the topics of AI and algorithmic biases.
She was a speaker at multiple Meetups and barcamps, and publishes blog posts about her
Machine Learning insights on Medium.
